data.title: Deborah "Debbie" Ann Orr Obituary 2023

data.text:
Deborah “Debbie” A Johnson Orr,age 65 of Maryville, TN passed peacefully on September 8, 2023. She was born February 18, 1958, in Colorado Springs, Colorado.

She was a beloved Mother, Grandmother, Great Grandmother, Sister, Aunt and Friend. Debbie loved her family with everything she had. She was an employee of Shoney’s in Maryville for over 30 years, and she loved her Shoney’s family. She loved her animals and always had a cup of coffee in her hand. Our Mom will be missed more than words can express.

She is preceded in death by parents, Leonard and Dorothy “Sue” Johnson; Beloved husband, Stephen Orr; Sister, Linda Spayd; mother and father-in-law, Nancy and Glenn Orr.
